text: Georgios Kalogiannidis is a Greek archer. He was born on 21 November 1982. Kalogiannidis competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Georgios KalogiannidisGeorgios KALOGIANNIDIS == References == Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Greek archers Category:Olympians for Greece
